[r]But it's unfortunate. The blueprints I saw in that world contained many things that could not be understood or realized with the technology of today's world. [l][r]
I think it's a real shame. At the time, I was only concerned with flying for practical purposes, and didn't try to understand the theories and designs that were of no use. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

